<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c2">(٢٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{الْبَارِئُ}</span> ... الَّذِي يُصْدِرُ خَلْقَهُ عَلَى الكَيْفِيَّةِ الَّتِي يَشَاؤُهَا.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">(٢٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{الْحُسْنَى}</span> ... الَّتِي لَا أَحْسَنَ مِنْهَا.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>